text.tna263b63: Jessica is a Bay Area native with more than twenty years of experience as a paralegal. Prior to joining Summit Defense, Jessica worked at a nationally-recognized immigration litigation firm. She also interned at the Contra Costa County Office of the Public Defender, representing defendants in criminal court proceedings, as well as the Habeas Corpus Resource Center, representing condemned inmates. She is a fluent Spanish-speaker.
